Source: ftp://ftp.sleepycat.com/releases/db-%v.tar.gz
Replaces: db, db3, db31 (<< 3.1.17-8), db4-ssl, db4, db41-ssl, db41, db42-ssl, db42, db43-ssl, db43, db44
